---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: About
description: Learn more about Sepideh Mansouri, her design background, and what guides her work.
---
<section class="page-hero">
  <div class="page-hero-copy">
    <p class="eyebrow">About</p>
    <h1>Designing with calm structure, empathy, and a strong sense of visual tone.</h1>
    {% for paragraph in site.about.summary %}
      <p class="page-lead">{{ paragraph }}</p>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
  <div class="page-hero-visual visual-swatch visual-swatch-coral">
    <span>Berlin based</span>
    <strong>UI/UX Designer</strong>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="split-section">
  <article class="content-card">
    <p class="eyebrow">What guides me</p>
    <h2>I want interfaces to feel capable, respectful, and easy to move through.</h2>
    <p>My background in content work and customer-facing roles taught me how much trust depends on clarity. In design, I bring that same attention to information structure, interaction flow, and the emotional tone of each screen.</p>
  </article>
  <aside class="note-card">
    <p class="eyebrow">Principles</p>
    <ul class="plain-list">
      {% for principle in site.about.principles %}
        <li>{{ principle }}</li>
      {% endfor %}
    </ul>
  </aside>
</section>

<section class="section-block">
  <div class="section-heading">
    <div>
      <p class="eyebrow">Working style</p>
      <h2>Research-minded, visually thoughtful, and collaborative.</h2>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="cards-grid">
    <article class="info-card">
      <p class="eyebrow">Listen</p>
      <h3>Understand the real problem</h3>
      <p>I like starting with user goals and context so the work solves what actually matters.</p>
    </article>
    <article class="info-card">
      <p class="eyebrow">Shape</p>
      <h3>Turn ideas into usable structure</h3>
      <p>I organize flows, content, and components so the product feels coherent and easier to use.</p>
    </article>
    <article class="info-card">
      <p class="eyebrow">Refine</p>
      <h3>Build trust through detail</h3>
      <p>I care about hierarchy, wording, and visual finish because small decisions shape confidence.</p>
    </article>
  </div>
</section>
